    <div class="post-title">

        <h5 class="mt10">5. Design filters to fit your site’s design</h5>

    </div>

    <p>The design here doesn’t refer to the visual design only. While it is important to customize filters to fit the
        visual elements of your site, keep in mind to create filters that reflect the nature of your site or the
        customers you want to target. Using categories like “work” or “party” can also serve as a buying guide for your
        customers.
    </p>

