        <h5 class="mt10">6. Apply filters without reloading</h5>

    </div>

    <p>Long loading times after customers select filters on your store leads to high exit rates. Having quick page
        reload is a great means of keeping customers engaged. While this might seem simple to accomplish, it can be
        quite difficult to implement especially on mobile. Improve search experience considerably with custom smart
        filters that are capable of delivering seamless experiences on all devices and OSs.
    </p>

